26#include "config.h"
27#include "AsyncRevalidation.h"
28
29#if ENABLE(NETWORK_CACHE_STALE_WHILE_REVALIDATE)
30#include <WebCore/CacheValidation.h>
31#include <WebCore/ResourceRequest.h>
32
33namespace WebKit {
34namespace NetworkCache {
35
36static inline WebCore::ResourceRequest constructRevalidationRequest(const Key& key, const WebCore::ResourceRequest& request, const Entry& entry)
37{
38 WebCore::ResourceRequest revalidationRequest = request;
39 if (!key.partition().isEmpty())
40 revalidationRequest.setCachePartition(key.partition());
41 ASSERT_WITH_MESSAGE(key.range().isEmpty(), "range is not supported");
42
43 revalidationRequest.makeUnconditional();
44 auto eTag = entry.response().httpHeaderField(WebCore::HTTPHeaderName::ETag);
45 if (!eTag.isEmpty())
46 revalidationRequest.setHTTPHeaderField(WebCore::HTTPHeaderName::IfNoneMatch, eTag);
47
48 auto lastModified = entry.response().httpHeaderField(WebCore::HTTPHeaderName::LastModified);
49 if (!lastModified.isEmpty())
50 revalidationRequest.setHTTPHeaderField(WebCore::HTTPHeaderName::IfModifiedSince, lastModified);
51
52 revalidationRequest.setPriority(WebCore::ResourceLoadPriority::Low);
53
54 return revalidationRequest;
55}
56
57void AsyncRevalidation::cancel()
58{
59 if (m_load)
60 m_load->cancel();
61}
62
63void AsyncRevalidation::staleWhileRevalidateEnding()
64{
65 if (m_completionHandler)
66 m_completionHandler(Result::Timeout);
67}
68
69AsyncRevalidation::AsyncRevalidation(Cache& cache, const GlobalFrameID& frameID, const WebCore::ResourceRequest& request, std::unique_ptr<NetworkCache::Entry>&& entry, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain> isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, CompletionHandler<void(Result)>&& handler)
70 : m_timer(*this, &AsyncRevalidation::staleWhileRevalidateEnding)
71 , m_completionHandler(WTFMove(handler))
72{
73 auto key = entry->key();
74 auto revalidationRequest = constructRevalidationRequest(key, request, *entry.get());
75 auto age = WebCore::computeCurrentAge(entry->response(), entry->timeStamp());
76 auto lifetime = WebCore::computeFreshnessLifetimeForHTTPFamily(entry->response(), entry->timeStamp());
77 auto responseMaxStaleness = entry->response().cacheControlStaleWhileRevalidate();
78 ASSERT(responseMaxStaleness);
79 m_timer.startOneShot(*responseMaxStaleness + (lifetime - age));
80 m_load = makeUnique<SpeculativeLoad>(cache, frameID, WTFMove(revalidationRequest), WTFMove(entry), isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, [this, key, revalidationRequest](auto&& revalidatedEntry) {
81 ASSERT(!revalidatedEntry || !revalidatedEntry->needsValidation());
82 ASSERT(!revalidatedEntry || revalidatedEntry->key() == key);
83 if (m_completionHandler)
84 m_completionHandler(revalidatedEntry ? Result::Success : Result::Failure);
85 });
86}
